reviewText: Clearly the best way to bring back the past, great is all I can say

The best and most factual look at the true Dinner Set Gang, the best jewel thief team in the country, who pulled off the largest home burglary in U.S. history. And it's the first time brothers-in-law and partners Pete Salerno & Dominick Latella ever appeared on camera in the same show, along with their twin-sister wives, to talk about their amazing exploits.
The story was nominated for an Emmy Award as Best News Feature, for 60 Minutes, correspondent Steve Kroft, and the producer Neeraj Khemlani.
